{
  "stem": "24409.11",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Not a passport-- a document in English and in Russian [INAUDIBLE] in our prisoner, a Russian who had worked with the German collaborators and was arrested there.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And he-- he immediately [INAUDIBLE] said the holder of this document-- I had one for all three and one for each individual.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Second Lieutenant William Perl is proceeding into Russian-- into Russian occupied territory on an important mission or allied personnel.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] [? asked ?] to be-- to this allied officer of utmost help.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So then when I came, I didn't go through the main checking point [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "There was a main-- main point [? for-- ?] and once I go a little further south [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And there-- there was on the bridge with the entry where on one side was an American guard.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "The other side was Russian.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the guys told me [INAUDIBLE] then they shot him in the heart.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They also [INAUDIBLE] military intelligence.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I told him what-- what-- what do you have to do there?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I said, [INAUDIBLE] confidential military [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Those became [INAUDIBLE] all about. the Russians.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I-- first of all, we-- we had loaded our jeep with all kinds of goodies for us, whiskey and cigarettes.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we distributed a ton of it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And one of the Russians jumped into the jeep and says, go.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I told you guys go now.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "To my horror, he drove up to the commander [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] they asked us [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And it appears.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And soon, he came back with that officer and the same lieutenant.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And this officer-- none of them spoke English, but at least that man spoke German.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Many of the Russians spoke German.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "The lieutenant spoke German too.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They had been fighting the Germans for a long time.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The Russians are very talented for languages.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
